{"tid":292510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人租緊樓住 又有養寵物？有事請教","createTime":"2017-06-21T12:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T14:10:01.000Z","uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b58f20d160b1ea6db1b11c8b6fc3b2fa838be2e","tid":292510,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n因為家庭原因<br />\n想搬出嚟住<br />\n但又唔知自己負唔負擔到<br />\n<br />\n想請問各位<br />\n有幾多人係自己搬出嚟住<br />\n我考慮緊租村屋 因為想養貓狗<br />\n我想知道大概租金佔收入幾多左右先應付到<br />\n<br />\n我上網搵到呢啲盤幾啱心水<br />\n有無人係住類似村屋 可以分享一下組驗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rent.591.com.hk/rent-detail-635592.html?fid=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frent.591.com.hk%2Frent-detail-635592.html%3Ffid%3D1&d=f%2B4lu%2FvI2JV00Q%2FlOQOp9hv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=cf5c5743\" target=\"_blank\">https://rent.591.com.hk/rent-detail-635592.html?fid=1</a><br />\n<br />\n（公屋不在此討論）"},{"pid":"cc5c788f62206a77b366e198ab88625aa967bd6f","tid":292510,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:35:26.000Z","msg":"你每月搵幾多先<br />\n<br />\n無收入怕你害死寵物"},{"pid":"b868fa0c15dab9271286a3e252d7cf1d9bcdc9f6","tid":292510,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你每月搵幾多先<br />\n<br />\n無收入怕你害死寵物</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 所以一定計過數 有能力先養<br />\n搵幾多盲無謂提 真係唔多<br />\n一般建議租金/養寵埋開支佔收入幾多先應付到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9c94dba060305c7c3f92fb2ba5813eac90da93","tid":292510,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269029f8f2a77884f6037c7f1e1ee5ad14650e61","tid":292510,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca4e75b1e12dd739f0c81cf923caa6e5b422fd8","tid":292510,"uid":123605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}